	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64247924">Down here in Belgium, it is by many considered as a waste of money for a simple economical reason. The costs of sun based waterheaters are close to that of a decent array of solar panels. When your water is at temperature, your water heating installation is useless. Solar panels keep delivering power that you can sell or store. In other words, you need to shower a lot to get an advantage out of it.</div>
	</div>

