			<h4><a id="comment_link_64248448" name="comment_link_64248448" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23230116&amp;cid=64248448" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64248448)" >Heat pump hot water from solar PV has advantages</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64248448" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64248448); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
